node.text:
Only two weekends left to watch a movie on the water!🛥📽(remaining line-up below ⬇️) Learn more + get tickets at BucketListers.com or our link-in-bio @LosAngelesBucketList. Who wants to go? 

- Friday, Sept 10: Blue Crush
- Saturday, Sept 11: Jaws
- Sunday, Sept 12: The Lion King
- Thursday, Sept 16: Jaws
- Friday, Sept 17: The Shallows
- Saturday, Sept 18: Pulp Fiction
- Sunday, Sept 19: Frozen II
#LAbucketlist #BoatCinema #LA #California

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by LA Bucket List 🌴 on September 09, 2021 tagging @losangelesbucketlist. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Who else needs a moment to relax & unwind? ✨🧘‍♀️🍷You can enjoy a 50-minute Hatha style yoga class overlooking scenic vineyards of Malibu + post wine. Learn more & book your spot at Bucketlisters.com or link-in-bio @LosAngelesBucketlist

node.text:
Westfield GIVEAWAY 🛍🎳🍿 To close out summer, we’ve partnered with @WestfieldSantaAnita to help you shop, play & entertain! Prize includes: $500 Westfield gift card, a private movie screening at AMC, 10 Fun Box tickets & 2 hours of Bowlero bowling (up to 10 people).
To Enter: 1. Tag your crew and 2. Follow @WestfieldSantaAnita
-- Giveaway not affiliated with IG, value $1200, will end on 11:59 EST 9/15. Selection details & terms: bit.ly/bucketlistterms
